      "cooked": "<aside class=\"onebox whitelistedgeneric\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/5/51f96cd5482735616cf1e2948cb2873ed95b3331.jpg\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n      <a href=\"https://peizazhe.com/2018/04/09/lobbying-for-ruzhdie/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"12:43PM - 09 April 2018\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Peizazhe të fjalës – 9 Apr 18</a>\n  </header>\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:600/481;\"><img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/peizazhe.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/noun_352888_13A89E.png?fit=600%2C481&amp;amp;ssl=1\" class=\"thumbnail\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://peizazhe.com/2018/04/09/lobbying-for-ruzhdie/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">LOBBYING FOR RUZHDIE</a></h3>\n\n<p>nga Arjan Shahini Ruzhdia, një fshat me disa qindra banorë në Fier, ka hyrë në historinë e zgjedhjeve elektorale në Shqipëri si epitomi i manipulimit të zgjedhjeve. Është pikërisht Ruzhdia, e çfarë…</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<p>Nuk e di  pse ky e quan lobiizem dhe jo lobizem.</p>\n<p>edhe disa grafike per inkuizitorin e madh, se i ka qejf …</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/7/7935829da485beb5e407296daf4639a5d02762fa.png\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/7935829da485beb5e407296daf4639a5d02762fa\" title=\"kliente_rajon.png\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/7/7935829da485beb5e407296daf4639a5d02762fa.png\" alt=\"kliente_rajon\" width=\"800\" height=\"538\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7935829da485beb5e407296daf4639a5d02762fa_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use x